Package: claude-voice
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: redrum
Installed-Size: 12
Depends: curl
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jerimie81/claude-voice-integration-apk
Description: Voice-triggered Claude CLI relay for Termux
 Enables Google Assistant (via Android App Actions) to relay voice queries
 to Claude CLI — either forwarded over HTTP to a PC running the companion
 Flask server, or executed locally inside Termux when claude CLI is installed.
 .
 Components:
  - /usr/bin/claude-voice  : main relay script (relay or local mode)
  - /usr/etc/claude-voice.conf : configuration file
